### Obtener todos los ítems (por defecto)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/
Accept: application/json

### Obtener ítems con parámetros de consulta (Query Params)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?skip=1&limit=1
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item por ID (sin query param q)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item por ID (con query param q)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc?q=hola
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item por ID (con espacios en q)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc?q=hola%20mundo
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item por ID (con q vacío)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc?q=
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item por ID (con caracteres especiales en q)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc?q=monitor%26teclado
Accept: application/json


### User item - sin query params (usa defaults)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/7/items/abc
Accept: application/json


### User item - con query param q
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/7/items/abc?q=hola
Accept: application/json


### User item - respuesta corta (short=true)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/7/items/abc?short=true
Accept: application/json


### User item - con q y short=true
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/7/items/abc?q=hola&short=true
Accept: application/json


### User item - short con otras variantes booleanas
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/7/items/abc?short=1
Accept: application/json

###
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/7/items/abc?short=true
Accept: application/json


### User item - error típico (user_id debe ser int)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/abc/items/xyz
Accept: application/json



### Query param requerido (needy) - OK
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items1/abc?needy=si
Accept: application/json


### Query param requerido (needy) - otro ejemplo
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items1/123?needy=pan
Accept: application/json


### Falta needy (debería dar 422 Unprocessable Entity)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items1/abc
Accept: application/json


### Needy con espacios (URL encoded)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc?needy=necesito%20algo
Accept: application/json


### Needy con caracteres especiales (ej: & debe ir codificado)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/abc?needy=monitor%20%26%20teclado
Accept: application/json
